snippet.title: Quite Soulless Trailer Version 3
snippet.description:
Hello! 

I am the mental patient (schizophrenic) without any human rights has escaped from the mental ward in Russia, and have not had any human rights like drive the car and manage the property, this is my anime about mental isolation ward (created in the most pieces 2006-2008), also I was subject to the chemical castration.

Russia started to give away the international travel documents to the mental patients as the democracy goes on and I went to the USA, there my asylum was denied and now I am subject to deportation back to the mental ward in Russia as of removal order of 7-15-2010 signed by indescent judge Isabel Bronzina.

Also I want to mention crazy nazi bitches US attorneys Sandra Anderson and Anwer Khan, and I remember attorney is smiling and saying in the end 'So you have no prove that you do not have any sort of psychosis'. I was saying in the court that I am not mentally sick, and I had the document of american doctor Bitar that my russian diagnosis was all 10 years wrong.

Watch!

Vasily Zotov
